  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Nepal Security Sector Network. Project period: 14.10.2009-13.10.2010. The NSSN will support the Nepali Government and national security institutions by systematically analyzing, producing, debating, and advocating policy recommendations on the issues of security sector governance on a national and regional level. The Network coordinates the intellectual leadership of Nepal&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s civil society, academia, researchers, and practitioners in order to create a sociopolitical consensus on policy issues and their solutions. The NSSN engages in the process that develops collaboration and even partnerships with concerned institutions and individuals responsible for decision and implementation of security issues. In this process NSSN works with the Nepali Government, Nepali civil society organizations and other international organizations. Project area: Kathmandu.</narrative>
  </description>
